articles.author: Laken Litman
articles.title: USA vs. England could change world's perception of American soccer - FOX Sports
articles.description: The USMNT has a chance to change the way American soccer is viewed. All it has to do? Get a win against England on Friday.
articles.content:
AL RAYYAN, Qatar This United States men's national team has been on a mission to shift the way the world perceives American soccer. 
And what better way to change minds than to beat England, a favor… [+5649 chars]
